@startuml
title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - USLP08

actor "Freight Manager" as FM
participant ":System" as System

autonumber

FM -> System : requestPendingFreights()
activate System
System --> FM : displayPendingFreightsList(freightList)
deactivate System

FM -> System : defineRouteType(simple | complex)
activate System
System --> FM : requestRouteDetails(selectedFreights, pathNodes)
deactivate System

FM -> System : submitRouteAssignment(freights, path)
activate System

note right of System
  The system processes the route.
  Simple: Single shipment (X to Y).
  Complex: Multiple shipments/stops.
end note

System --> FM : displayPlannedRoute(stationSequence, cargoOperationsList)
deactivate System

@enduml